{"tid":784934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（冇圖純學術討論）點解啲大波港女對自己對波咁唔自豪","createTime":"2018-08-18T17:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T17:52:30.000Z","uid":49661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9f1706cb5555047d055f94ac3f522af0a40bc140","tid":784934,"uid":49661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"見到隔離po啲絲打問點樣著衫可以遮咗個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔理你肥又好瘦又好，大波都己經係優勢<br />\n肥底大波 唔緊要，可以減肥變肉地大波/瘦底大波<br />\n瘦底大波 恭喜你<br />\n<br />\n絲打們唔好畀身邊啲ipad港女fd洗腦覺得大波唔好大波著衫唔好睇呀<br />\n大波著衫不知幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我哋有先天嘅優勢點解唔show出嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係妒忌人 <br />\n利申：絲32大D 唔算大但過得去 好羨慕啲大波星人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大波星人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好睇樣 淨係副body己經好 撚 正<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/013650_ec8f2fef6a1cb3362930a3d89370f366.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F013650_ec8f2fef6a1cb3362930a3d89370f366.png&h=f87f26af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/013656_4934abb698c53c58a3d38078093f68c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F013656_4934abb698c53c58a3d38078093f68c1.png&h=b9b979e4&s={SIZE}\" /><b